# URL Shortener API Tests
# Run with: httpie --session=./session.json < api-requests.http

### Shorten URL with expiration
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/data/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "longUrl": "https://www.example.com/very/long/url/path",
  "expiresAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

### Shorten URL without expiration
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/data/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "longUrl": "https://www.google.com/search?q=url+shortener"
}

### Redirect to original URL (replace {shortUrl} with actual short URL)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/{shortUrl}
Accept: application/json

### Get analytics for short URL (replace {shortUrl} with actual short URL)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/analytics/{shortUrl}
Accept: application/json

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### API Documentation
GET http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html

### Application Info
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/info

### Application Metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics

### Specific Metric (JVM Memory)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/jvm.memory.used

### Health Component (Database)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health/db